## LogicCAD

This was my graduation project from the college of computer engineering. It's a simulation software
for logic circuits, which allows designing and running logic circuits. The software includes basic
logic gates like AND and OR among others, and it allows the user to built new components that can
then be re-used to build bigger and more complicated circuits.

The software was built for MS Windows using C++ and MFC.

![](/الموارد/لوجك_كاد.gif)
